to the audience on stage, Naoki.

21
00:04:41.281 --> 00:04:42.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It exposes your lack of intelligence.

22
00:04:42.448 --> 00:04:44.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let’s add songs to our encore.

23
00:04:44.701 --> 00:04:46.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
