Don’t be ridiculous.

25
00:04:49.455 --> 00:04:52.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That’ll be impossible.
We’re approaching our time limit here.

26
00:04:52.166 --> 00:04:54.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We’re not renting
this hall for free, you know.

27
00:04:54.502 --> 00:04:58.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
For a manager,
you can be really stingy, Take.

28
00:04:59.841 --> 00:05:02.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Reira, you shouldn’t talk either.

29
00:05:07.473 --> 00:05:10.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, Ren, you know
you made a mistake in the second song.

30
00:05:10.810 --> 00:05:12.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You might’ve thought you got away with it,
but that was pretty obvious…

31
00:05:13.646 --> 00:05:14.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where are you going, Ren?

32
00:05:14.814 --> 00:05:15.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
To take a piss!

33
00:05:17.692 --> 00:05:21.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Where’d he make a mistake?
I didn’t notice anything.

34
00:05:21.446 --> 00:05:23.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So even Ren can make a mistake, I guess.

35
00:05:23.698 --> 00:05:27.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Notice it, damn it.</i>
<i>What is it with our band members?</i>

36
00:05:27.910 --> 00:05:34.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Encore! Encore! Encore! Encore!

37
00:05:34.334 --> 00:05:39.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hasn’t Ren noticed that you’re here?

38
00:05:40.048 --> 00:05:43.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He’s not likely able to see the audience
with all those spotlights.

39
00:05:43.092 --> 00:05:45.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Really?
-Well, I can’t speak from experience.

40
00:05:45.470 --> 00:05:47.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’ve never performed on a stage this big.

41
00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:48.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>No way! He can't see us?</i>

42
00:05:49.015 --> 00:05:51.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>But we’re sitting in the first row.</i>
<i>Can’t he see a little?</i>

43
00:05:51.601 --> 00:05:53.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Oh, this may be a trap</i>
<i>set up by the Demon Lord.</i>

44
00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:58.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It must feel really good,
singing in such a big place.

45
00:06:03.988 --> 00:06:05.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You’ll be able to…</i>

46
00:06:06.866 --> 00:06:08.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Being you, Nana, I’m sure you will.</i>

47
00:06:10.119 --> 00:06:13.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>The band BLAST will surpass Trapnest!</i>

48
00:06:25.468 --> 00:06:27.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Yes.
-Yasu, Nana’s here!

49
00:06:29.305 --> 00:06:32.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Right. Is the concert over already?

50
00:06:32.141 --> 00:06:34.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It’s not over.</i>
<i>We’re about to go out for the encore.</i>

51
00:06:35.311 --> 00:06:36.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Well, good luck with that.</i>

52
00:06:37.021 --> 00:06:39.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You knew about this, didn’t you?
Why didn’t you tell me?

53
00:06:39.941 --> 00:06:41.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I wanted it to be a surprise.</i>

54
00:06:41.609 --> 00:06:43.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then you succeeded.
I even made a mistake on stage.

55
00:06:43.945 --> 00:06:45.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Although I faked it
with a little rearrangement.

56
00:06:46.781 --> 00:06:48.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Really? That’s even more than
I could’ve asked for.

57
00:06:48.616 --> 00:06:49.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It’s not a laughing matter!</i>

58
00:06:50.284 --> 00:06:52.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If it were in Tokyo, that’s one thing,

59
00:06:52.203 --> 00:06:53.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but what’s she doing
out here in the countryside?

60
00:06:53.913 --> 00:06:55.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not to mention the front row.

61
00:06:55.414 --> 00:06:57.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Then jump off the stage and embrace her.</i>

62
00:06:57.792 --> 00:06:58.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You can’t expect me to do that!

63
00:06:59.877 --> 00:07:02.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ren! What are you shouting about?

64
00:07:02.088 --> 00:07:03.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don’t lose it yet.
We’re not done with the performance!

65
00:07:03.881 --> 00:07:05.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We're going out for the encore.

66
00:07:05.925 --> 00:07:10.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Go. I’ll email you the cell number</i>
<i>of the girl Nana’s with.</i>

67
00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:13.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If you wanna see Nana, call that number.

68
00:07:17.395 --> 00:07:20.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How can I face her after what happened?

69
00:07:22.900 --> 00:07:27.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I’m tired of hearing you say that.</i>
<i>You can be such a drag sometimes.</i>

70
00:07:29.323 --> 00:07:31.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If you don’t intend to see her…

71
00:07:31.993 --> 00:07:33.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’ll take Nana for myself.

72
00:07:36.330 --> 00:07:37.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ren, we’re going!

73
00:07:50.386 --> 00:07:52.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Welcome home. You must be hungry.

74
00:07:53.598 --> 00:07:55.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dinner is ready.

75
00:07:58.686 --> 00:08:00.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>They played two songs for the encore.</i>

76
00:08:01.063 --> 00:08:04.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Ren didn’t glance over our way even once.</i>

77
00:08:06.402 --> 00:08:10.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is making me really nervous,
having a meal with such a cute girl.

78
00:08:10.615 --> 00:08:11.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>A cute girl?</i>

79
00:08:11.699 --> 00:08:15.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What are you saying, Dad?
You perverted old man.

80
00:08:15.620 --> 00:08:19.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What! You’re one to talk,
with that Tarzan outfit.

81
00:08:19.207 --> 00:08:21.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Tarzan?
-Go back to the jungle!

82
00:08:24.003 --> 00:08:26.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It was as if I had awakened from a dream.</i>

83
00:08:28.508 --> 00:08:31.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>We were reminded once and for all</i>
<i>that Ren is now a superstar</i>

84
00:08:31.594 --> 00:08:35.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>and out of our reach.</i>

85
00:08:35.431 --> 00:08:37.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It made me feel miserable.</i>

86
00:08:40.144 --> 00:08:41.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That was refreshing.

87
00:08:41.646 --> 00:08:43.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The bath’s available, Nana.

88
00:08:43.606 --> 00:08:45.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I left towels out for you.

89
00:08:45.858 --> 00:08:47.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sure. Thanks.

90
00:09:16.222 --> 00:09:19.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Oh, darn! I forgot to switch it back on.</i>

91
00:09:19.725 --> 00:09:20.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
