SUBJECT: CONFIDENTIAL

93
00:09:22.144 --> 00:09:23.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Yasu?</i>

94
00:09:23.729 --> 00:09:26.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>That’s unusual. What could it be?</i>

95
00:09:28.985 --> 00:09:32.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
REN MIGHT BE GIVING YOU A CALL.

96
00:09:41.455 --> 00:09:42.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nana! Big news!

97
00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:45.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know, you shouldn’t barge in
when someone’s taking a bath…

98
00:09:46.043 --> 00:09:47.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But this really is big news!

99
00:09:47.461 --> 00:09:48.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Another murder?

100
00:09:48.713 --> 00:09:51.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No! Look here! Yasu sent me an e-mail!

101
00:09:51.465 --> 00:09:52.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yasu?

102
00:09:54.719 --> 00:09:57.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Sorry, Nana! I forgot</i>
<i>to switch my phone back on</i>

103
00:09:57.096 --> 00:09:59.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>because it had to be</i>
<i>switched off in the hall.</i>

104
00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:02.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It’s past midnight.
He may have tried to call.

105
00:10:02.435 --> 00:10:04.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What’s the meaning of this?
Why would Yasu…

106
00:10:05.062 --> 00:10:08.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don’t know.
Maybe Yasu gave Ren my number.

107
00:10:08.190 --> 00:10:10.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But Ren was unreachable, wasn’t he?

108
00:10:10.610 --> 00:10:13.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don’t really understand,
but what should we do?

109
00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:18.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Call Yasu.

110
00:10:29.086 --> 00:10:30.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-<i>Hello.</i>
-Hello, Yasu. It’s me.

111
00:10:31.005 --> 00:10:35.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hello, Nana. Sorry about
giving out your number without asking.

112
00:10:35.384 --> 00:10:36.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>No problem.</i>

113
00:10:36.510 --> 00:10:37.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did Ren call?

114
00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:38.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I’m not sure.</i>

115
00:10:38.846 --> 00:10:40.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did you check your missed calls?

116
00:10:40.723 --> 00:10:43.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I forgot to turn
the phone back on after the concert.

117
00:10:43.851 --> 00:10:45.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-<i>What?</i>
-I wonder if Ren’s already called.

118
00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:47.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Who knows?

119
00:10:47.229 --> 00:10:48.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What’ll I do?</i>

120
00:10:48.981 --> 00:10:51.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just wait and I’m sure he’ll call again.

121
00:10:51.817 --> 00:10:52.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Really?</i>

122
00:10:53.277 --> 00:10:56.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Probably. I provoked him a bit.

123
00:10:57.031 --> 00:10:59.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Don’t joke around, baldy!</i>

124
00:10:59.492 --> 00:11:03.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don’t know what you told Ren,
but mind your own business.

125
00:11:03.746 --> 00:11:06.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I have nothing to say
to him at this point.

126
00:11:06.582 --> 00:11:07.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, let me make one thing clear.

127
00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:12.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It was he who called me
after noticing you at the concert hall.

128
00:11:13.339 --> 00:11:16.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I just gave him the phone number.</i>

129
00:11:16.092 --> 00:11:18.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>If you have nothing to say to him,</i>
<i>tell him that directly.</i>

130
00:11:19.512 --> 00:11:21.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If you have no need for the key
to the place you and Ren used to live

131
00:11:22.056 --> 00:11:27.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and the key to the padlock
around Ren’s neck, just get rid of them.

132
00:11:27.228 --> 00:11:29.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That would put an end to everything.

133
00:11:29.980 --> 00:11:31.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Put yourself in his shoes.</i>

134
00:11:31.982 --> 00:11:35.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>He’s bound by a woman</i>
<i>he can never have again.</i>

135
00:11:48.082 --> 00:11:49.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I understand.

136
00:11:50.418 --> 00:11:52.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Give me Ren’s cell number.

137
00:11:53.212 --> 00:11:55.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’m not the type to sit around and wait.

138
00:12:04.682 --> 00:12:06.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
